data.description: Welcome to your Chantal Estates dream home with a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. This light and bright residence features 4 spacious beds, 3 baths, 3 car garage, double gates with R.V access, elect outlet 50 amp, as you step into this serene abode you'll be captivated by the high ceilings, open-concept kitchen w granite countertops, a huge custom walking closet, double rain shower, last but not least sparkling pool w built-in Baja step, dual pergolas perfect for those family gatherings!! Call today
